Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{Phantom 23}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.42,0:02:03.85,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Stop lazing around, transfer student!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.41,0:02:05.59,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's clean up time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.04,0:02:15.98,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He's a weird guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.98,0:02:20.67,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't know what he's seeing, sometimes he just spaces out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.67,0:02:23.99,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He looks a bit clumsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.73,0:02:27.89,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Lucky, the rain stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.07,0:02:30.46,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's pretty, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.04,0:02:34.21,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I was about to miss it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.51,0:02:39.54,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Because it's a scenery of nature,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.16,0:02:42.93,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}we often overlook it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.45,0:02:55.94,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The ship will set sail on Monday midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.78,0:03:01.53,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There's people that will pick us up at the hotel, so we have to stay there until the evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.29,0:03:06.70,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just five more days living here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.33,0:03:09.95,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I hope no one tries to stop us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.72,0:03:12.21,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.50,0:03:17.37,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You should prepare for the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.23,0:03:19.90,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't want to do this again...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.53,0:03:25.92,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If only we could disappear like mist...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.92,0:03:26.89,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.09,0:03:38.03,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Scythe!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.65,0:03:43.74,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What is it, Ms. Garland?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.74,0:03:45.73,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Where's Phantom?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.73,0:03:48.54,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You better not be scheming something again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.99,0:03:50.70,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Phantom?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.70,0:03:55.29,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wasn't she supposed to be with you today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.63,0:03:57.43,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I lost her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.43,0:04:00.43,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Damn, just when I took my eyes off her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.43,0:04:03.11,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's not like something will happen today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.11,0:04:05.26,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm sure she will come back tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.26,0:04:08.01,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The armory is almost empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.53,0:04:12.22,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh... that's a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.22,0:04:14.27,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What is she planning to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.17,0:04:19.94,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh well, I know a place where she'll probably show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.98,0:04:26.66,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Contact McGuire and Mr. Shiga and tell them I'll go look for Phantom immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.48,0:04:35.18,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So the dice have been cast.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.15,0:05:00.68,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She's just a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.68,0:05:02.65,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.16,0:05:06.97,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm over taking over where Zwei left off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.79,0:05:08.95,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.20,0:05:21.49,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Drei?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.49,0:05:24.76,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yep. That's my name from today on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.53,0:05:27.81,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nice to meet you, Miss Experienced!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.81,0:05:30.22,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Can you cover my back?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.22,0:05:42.09,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.48,0:05:46.70,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You won't run away, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:58.46,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}God, I'm not good at babysitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.07,0:06:09.87,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm sorry about what happened a few days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.87,0:06:12.05,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I surprised you pretty badly, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.05,0:06:13.43,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.54,0:06:26.06,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Back then abroad, she...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.06,0:06:32.45,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well, I never thought she'd chase me here... \Nand I never expected her to punch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.60,0:06:47.01,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But I'm glad I could meet her again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.49,0:06:54.55,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She hit me, but I think we had a good talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.34,0:06:58.06,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's over between me and her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.14,0:07:01.06,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.84,0:07:03.70,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll make up for it next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.70,0:07:05.38,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We could go to the cinema again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.28,0:07:07.13,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:09.08,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.08,0:07:09.78,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.13,0:07:25.22,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.22,0:07:26.34,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why is it dark?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.78,0:07:31.01,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ah, mom won't be home today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.45,0:07:49.79,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hi. It's not the first time we meet,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.79,0:07:51.99,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}so don't be so wary.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.39,0:07:54.77,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.77,0:07:57.79,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You are Godou's little princess, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.27,0:08:00.33,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Eh? Godou?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.46,0:08:03.79,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Are you talking about my uncle?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.15,0:08:06.33,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Uncle?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.23,0:08:08.68,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh well,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.68,0:08:10.63,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll leave the dry explanations for later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.61,0:08:12.38,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.08,0:08:18.20,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You might not see one every day in this country,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.20,0:08:19.56,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but yeah, it's a real gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:23.94,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Get on the bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.36,0:08:28.34,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll tell you something about your beloved...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.93,0:08:32.19,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...Reiji's secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.95,0:10:00.95,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I thought you'd show up, Phantom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.67,0:10:12.87,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wait for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.86,0:10:14.88,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nice timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.48,0:10:17.79,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I need to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.61,0:10:20.34,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Cal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.72,0:10:22.81,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The game's on again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.81,0:10:25.80,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No one touches Zwei and Ein.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.80,0:10:28.31,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you can't promise that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.33,0:10:32.77,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...I'll kill the little princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.41,0:10:39.15,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I won't let anyone interfere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.15,0:10:41.56,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't lay a finger on my target!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.56,0:10:44.45,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How many stupid things will you do until you're satisfied?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.88,0:10:49.16,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Do you hate Zwei that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.65,0:10:51.90,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You bet I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.68,0:10:57.83,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No matter if it's a traitor or someone who harms civilians,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.83,0:11:00.01,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can never forgive them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.80,0:11:07.81,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There are lines you mustn't cross.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.38,0:11:18.74,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Open your eyes, Cal. Once you go past this point, you will fall into a bottomless abyss.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.93,0:11:24.17,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I've been wondering all the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.68,0:11:29.91,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Lizzie, why were you so nice to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.90,0:11:35.53,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Both Zwei and me didn't want you to become an assassin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.09,0:11:38.63,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So I felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.09,0:11:42.13,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Everyone is so selfish...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.45,0:11:45.42,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm Phantom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.42,0:11:48.60,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you have a problem, just try and stop me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.60,0:11:50.14,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Right here, right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.61,0:12:09.66,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Once the melody is over, I'll draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.05,0:12:19.08,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you don't pull the trigger before that, you're a sentimental idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.58,0:12:24.05,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're destined to die here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.13,0:13:02.84,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Cal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.43,0:13:04.11,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.34,0:13:09.85,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't want to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.72,0:14:02.11,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Cal!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.27,0:14:22.07,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why couldn't you pull the trigger?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.90,0:14:34.60,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why didn't I shoot?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.98,0:14:42.78,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Are you sure you want such a heavy gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.78,0:14:46.98,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, I don't want to shoot easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.25,0:14:53.26,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yet, this gun... this gun...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.75,0:14:58.31,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...is getting so heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.44,0:15:02.57,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...too heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.52,0:15:07.13,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Clau...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.71,0:15:29.66,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You'll be here for three or four days, so ration it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.66,0:15:32.60,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.18,0:15:36.92,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Please tell me the reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.92,0:15:40.96,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why go so far as killing people?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.49,0:15:48.00,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.99,0:15:55.47,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is the last of your friends you contacted, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.10,0:15:59.98,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This Kanji... you read it as "Reiji", don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.26,0:16:03.73,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Who are you to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.07,0:16:05.56,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}His ex-disciple...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.51,0:16:08.32,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...and his ex-lover.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.65,0:16:10.36,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.34,0:16:16.05,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why do you think that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.05,0:16:19.24,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What do you think you know about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.97,0:16:22.37,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.23,0:16:27.34,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I learned how to use this from Reiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.13,0:16:32.72,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What did you think he was doing in America?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.26,0:16:37.41,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He's an assassin... and an extraordinary one at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.37,0:16:41.81,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't think I can count the people Reiji killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.51,0:16:44.17,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.17,0:16:46.20,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're being played with.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.51,0:16:51.82,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Two years ago a man called Godou Daisuke was killed in Los Angeles.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.82,0:16:55.02,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You said he was your uncle, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.02,0:16:56.79,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why do you know this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.79,0:16:59.88,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm well informed. Better than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.71,0:17:04.66,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The truth is that he was a gang member,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.06,0:17:07.98,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and the story about him being your uncle is bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.98,0:17:12.17,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}In reality he was your brother from a different mother, and I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.27,0:17:15.09,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.46,0:17:20.76,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What? You don't like being the daughter of a mafia man?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.76,0:17:23.64,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There's even more to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.64,0:17:27.36,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Godou Daisuke's death wasn't an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.22,0:17:31.06,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Your precious Reiji as good as killed-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.06,0:17:32.89,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't make up stories!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.11,0:17:39.91,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's up to you to believe it or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.91,0:17:45.50,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But one day you will have to believe it, and your life will be stained with blood and death.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.38,0:17:49.07,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}When that time comes, remember the stories I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.07,0:17:51.75,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}All I've said is the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.12,0:17:56.21,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What is your goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.69,0:17:59.59,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To have a fight to the death...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.38,0:18:01.37,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...with Reiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.07,0:18:04.35,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}One will kill the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.40,0:18:06.59,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.95,0:18:09.30,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The day will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.73,0:18:13.57,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Come, it's the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.50,0:18:24.77,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.77,0:18:26.45,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sorry, but this isn't Mio speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.51,0:18:30.12,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What happened to Mio?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.12,0:18:34.13,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Calm down, I have no intention of hurting her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.03,0:18:37.23,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}While you're busy running away,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.23,0:18:40.82,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I thought I would take the burden of your hostage off your shoulders.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.82,0:18:42.84,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm doing you a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.84,0:18:45.87,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wasn't I supposed to be your only target?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.87,0:18:47.52,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mio doesn't have anything to do with...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.52,0:18:49.70,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You wanted to go back...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.40,0:18:51.52,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...to being honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.71,0:18:55.03,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}According to your wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.65,0:18:58.04,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...I'm protecting your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.69,0:19:03.00,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I won't let the Godou clan or Inferno get in your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.74,0:19:08.75,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}As long as you go to school, you will be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.75,0:19:13.04,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But there won't be any sudden disappearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.04,0:19:15.47,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't know where you could run away to...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.47,0:19:18.76,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But if you go somewhere out of my reach,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.76,0:19:22.88,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mio will go meet her brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.88,0:19:24.25,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Remember that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.25,0:19:27.35,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll always keep an eye on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.79,0:19:29.17,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This time...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.57,0:19:32.06,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...you won't be able to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.29,0:19:34.44,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This time...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.06,0:19:40.11,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can't believe she even went as far as to disobey Inferno.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.32,0:19:45.62,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's proof of how much she detests me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.20,0:19:48.58,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We should take a different path.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.58,0:19:49.60,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A different path?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.70,0:20:04.01,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh my, oh my...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.51,0:20:10.08,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It seems Phantom has kidnapped Mio.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.08,0:20:13.98,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just how far does your ego go?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.98,0:20:16.47,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}As I thought, you're well informed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.47,0:20:17.83,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't fuck with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.83,0:20:20.76,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is your plotting, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.76,0:20:21.65,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm afraid not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.96,0:20:25.52,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She is brother's memento.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.52,0:20:27.16,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She's not your toy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.75,0:20:30.44,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Your words might affect the treaty with Inferno.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.24,0:20:35.27,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I won't let the abduction of Fujieda Mio ruin that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.08,0:20:41.63,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll go ahead and search for Drei.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.63,0:20:45.19,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}As per her instructions, remain still.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.19,0:20:48.30,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I will shoot Drei and free Mio.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.30,0:20:51.22,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We're being monitored, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.22,0:20:54.14,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If we try to save Mio by force, she'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.48,0:20:59.35,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If I disappear alone, I'm sure Drei won't harm Mio.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.35,0:21:00.98,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why are you so sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.92,0:21:05.24,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Her target is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.06,0:21:06.90,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.05,0:21:10.15,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We aren't cornered yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.32,0:21:13.30,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Conquer your emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.30,0:21:14.95,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.38,0:21:18.64,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...you will perish.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.26,0:21:24.46,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Rest assured, Mr. Shiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.46,0:21:27.55,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I have already summoned my staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.40,0:21:33.00,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They are my ultimate soldiers, perfectly trained and controlled.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.00,0:21:35.69,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A will that crushed emotion...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.69,0:21:40.06,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...lets them finish any job they are assigned.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.44,0:21:52.48,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I will achieve the results you desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.62,0:21:57.00,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They cannot fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.93,0:23:38.07,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you live on...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.14,0:23:40.27,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...that would be my...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.41,0:23:43.10,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...proof I ever lived.
